From 99f4e10c535a2f173c3228b0e57b8f54aed19533 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: EricYang-wiwynn <Eric_Yang@wiwynn.com>
Date: Fri, 14 Feb 2025 16:48:08 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] platform-mc: Revert discovery FRU data

Found that in commit platform-mc: discovery FRU data from terminus,
b6d3943d0deca9e61826370f69c1309007a5a4aa, the interface information
under the PLDM inventory object causes the entity manager to take
longer than expected to complete Inventory added, resulting in the
MCTP EID probe taking too long.

As a short-term workaround, this commit is being reverted.
